      "lineNumber": 15,
      "sourceStatus": "REDACTION_MARKER_CHECK",
      "sourceText": "As of further interest to the Bureau in this regard, there is transmitted herewith photostatic copies of three letters dated August 4, 1947 and entitled \"Investigation of Flying Discs,\" furnished to me by [REDACTED] S, A-2, Army Air Forces, Hamilton Field, California, who is acting in the absence of [REDACTED] enclosing copies of reports of additional reported sightings of flying discs by persons in Oregon and Arizona, together with the results of their investigations in that regard.",
